{"tid":847591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★侍產假「一日都嫌多」！老闆心態：最好返365日工","createTime":"2018-10-04T09:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T13:04:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a01c1b188b165d46bd5cc61ac6635f8e581b8dea","tid":847591,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/173250_2a469c642b5658d0899fb318b3595ee4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F173250_2a469c642b5658d0899fb318b3595ee4.png&h=84c15b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府日前建議將男性侍產假由3日，增加到5日，代表飲食界老闆的行政會議成員張宇人稱，「侍產假一日都唔應該有。」言論一出，各方譁然。<br />\n<br />\n有新手父母表示失望，「老闆心態係一日假期都唔想畀，最好返晒365日工」，認為一個家庭，父母要共同分擔，加上媽媽產後承受極大壓力，「生完頭幾日會好唔開心，老公喺身邊，心會舒服好多」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/243024/%E4%BE%8D%E7%94%A2%E5%81%87-%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E9%83%BD%E5%AB%8C%E5%A4%9A-%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D-%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E5%BF%83%E6%85%8B-%E6%9C%80%E5%A5%BD%E8%BF%94365%E6%97%A5%E5%B7%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F243024%2F%25E4%25BE%258D%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2581%2587-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%25AB%258C%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D-%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2585%258B-%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%25BF%2594365%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25B7%25A5&d=8BteI%2Bf9ky9hy%2B9tl%2BrAfYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=cc9c521e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/243024/%E4%BE%8D%E7%94%A2%E5%81%87-%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E9%83%BD%E5%AB%8C%E5%A4%9A-%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D-%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E5%BF%83%E6%85%8B-%E6%9C%80%E5%A5%BD%E8%BF%94365%E6%97%A5%E5%B7%A5</a>"},{"pid":"e3229ee1fa5d930